description: Days from a key election, President Alexander Lukashenko accuses Russia of a violent plot.
title: Belarus ruler Lukashenko says Russia lying over 'mercenaries'
title_page: Belarus ruler Lukashenko says Russia lying over 'mercenaries' - BBC News
maintext: Mr Lukashenko, in power since 1994, has been criticised over his handling of the economy and the coronavirus pandemic. He has urged Belarusians to carry on as normal, scorning the lockdowns imposed by the rest of Europe to curb the virus.
